channel.title: error after starting electrum on whonix
channel.description: Hi there. There is an error in command line while i trying to start electrum on whonix-workstation. ./electrum-3.3.8-x86_64.AppImage (python3.6:5767): dbind-WARNING **: 08:29:50.310: Error retrieving accessibility bus address: org.freedesktop.DBus.Error.ServiceUnknown: The name org.a11y.Bus was not provided by any .service files is that ok?
